				\begin{document}$$^{{\circledR }}$$\end{document}® MD software (Osirix Foundation, Geneva, Switzerland). This software is FDA-cleared, CE-labelled for primary diagnostics, and is commonly used in medical AM. Osirix\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
